        <h2>blogcritics.org - Jack Goodstein - Oct. 30, 2014</h2>
        <p>Gabriel Espinosa and Hendrik Meurkens - 'Samba Little Samba'</p>
        <p>Demonstrating yet once more after their initial successful collaboration on Celebrando that you don't need to be a Brazilian to have an authentic feel for Brazilian jazz, Mexican bassist Gabriel Espinosa and harmonica/vibes master Hendrik Meurkens are scheduled to release their second album Samba Little Samba on November 11, 2014. </p>
